<div class="consequence-text">
<p>A few weeks into your doubled-up living arrangement, your wife goes into labor. Complications arise, and the doctors determine she needs an emergency C-section. The surgery goes well, and you have a healthy baby, but your wife's recovery will be more difficult than expected.</p>

<p>She needs help - real help - for the next several weeks. The cramped apartment, the other family, the stress of hiding from the landlord... it's all weighing heavily on both of you.</p>
</div>

<hr>

<h4>How will you handle this situation?</h4>

<div class="housing-choice">
<<link "Ask about bringing in your wife's friend for help">>
