<</link>>
<p><em>Your wife invited her friend from the shelter for additional help. You ask the family you are doubling up with if they would mind having an additional person in the house, but they are unsure and ask for time to decide. Do you bring the friend in despite not having an answer?</em></p>
</div>

<hr>

<div class="housing-choice">
<<link "Make adjustments yourselves">>
    <<goto "WorkLessPayMore">>
<</link>>
<p><em>Your wife needs additional help to prevent post-partum medical issues, which would be highly expensive and put a strain on the family. Do you take less jobs to have additional time to help your wife, or offer to pay more of the rent in exchange for the wife of the other family helping her in your absence?</em></p>
</div>


